        class="cta-button"
      >
        📄 Harvest Moon - Steel Guitar I
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1TmVpdZmrM7TS7xqlXLhVN2AHjssxOsf7"
        class="cta-button"
        download
        class="cta-button"
      >
        📄 Harvest Moon - Komplettes Arrangement als ZIP
